--- !u!1001 &246666633
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[0]
      value: 'Hana: Has the Sakura bloomed again? I can smell my love''s scent on
        the wind.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[1]
      value: 'Hana: Year after year, even the memory of their fragrance seems to
        lose its color.......In the end, is time too cruel, or am I too stubborn?'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[2]
      value: "Hana: The weight of grief held me here. I can\u2019t move on."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[3]
      value: "Hana: My dearest Matt and I promised beneath a Sakura Tree that every
        spring he would bring me a spray of the first blossoms\u2026. just like when
        we first met."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[4]
      value: 'Hana: You see, the seasons keep their word. They never fail to bring
        spring back. But the spring within my memories......has never returned.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 374185678237159095, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[5]
      value: 'Hana: Perhaps....... I have been clinging to that wish too tightly.
        So......could you bring me a spray of Sakura? Not for him. But to properly
        bid farewell the spring in which we met.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5706802075633393086, guid: cb2a8c88faef34a4aaf4b746b422abb8, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_SizeDelta.x
      value: 789.7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
